Fabio&amp;#039;s live radio show on London&amp;#039;s Kiss FM, recorded 12-2am 17th November 1995 (so probably the 18th really) by myself.

NOTE: This is Fabio DJing his radio show, not an in-the-mix set.

NOTE: The previous Fabio, Grooverider and Bukem tapes I was seeding were withdrawn because I renamed the files which broke the seeding. I&amp;#039;ll re-post them at some point.

------------------------------------------------------------------------

Recording Equipment:

1995: Denon TU260L Tuner --&gt; Yamaha KX580 tape deck --&gt; TDK SA audio cassette

2008: Yamaha KX383 tape deck --&gt; Soundblaster Live card --&gt; Audacity 1.3.4 --&gt; FLAC

------------------------------------------------------------------------

